{"word":"τάφρος","slug":"τάφρος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>τάφρος</b></el> <el>(τάφρος, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:θάπτω'><el>θάπτω</el></a>\n<p/><i>a ditch, trench</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>τάφρον ὀρύσσειν</el> <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>τ. ἐλαύνειν</el> to draw <i>a trench</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/>"}]}